    Scope and Contents
Included in this series are the Public Affairs papers, which are published by the Public Sector Program Evaluation Center.  File includes: Paper #1: "Reports on the 1972 Summer Institute on Interracial Education, by Augustine Stevens. Paper #2: "On the need for Central Dispatching on Emergency Ambulance Services in Sangamon County: Final Report.  Paper #3: "Bibliography  in Program Evaluation"  by Dana Barlow.   Paper #4:  "Program Evaluation in Illinois State Government: a Survey Report."  Paper #5: "Program Evaluation in State Government: Papers presented at Program Evaluation Conference", April 23, 1974.  Also included in this file is "The Changing Face of State Finance" published by the American Society for Public Administration (Central Illinois Chapter).  
  
